tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE labeled_training_data (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  feature_1 FLOAT,
  feature_2 FLOAT,
  label VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE labeled_training_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    input_data TEXT,
    label TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE training_statistics (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    training_id INT,
    loss FLOAT,
    accuracy FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE model_parameters (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    parameter_key TEXT,
    parameter_value TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE model_architecture (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    layer_name TEXT,
    activation_function TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE model_evaluation (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    evaluation_id INT,
    evaluation_metric TEXT,
    value FLOAT
)
